platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: 遊戲與睡眠追蹤工具合二為一，讓你在睡覺時就能輕鬆收集 Pokémon。
昼寝をしながらポケモンを集めましょう。睡眠記録アプリの機能を備えた魅力あふれるゲームです。
這款別具創意的遊戲結合了睡眠追蹤與寶可夢的魅力，讓你在睡夢中蒐集可愛的寶可夢，實現訓練家的「夢想」。
Now we can collect Pokémon literally while we nap? This charming blend of game and sleep tracker makes our dreams come true.

Inspired by the popular education method based on a sensory and kinetic way of learning, this app provides a variety of activities to guide children ages 3–7 as they embark on their first steps in the world of schooling.

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: ポケモンの寝顔をゲットできる 睡眠アプリ
